event.title: Shin Urayasu International Preschool's Candle Night
event.description:
Come enjoy a night of relaxation out at the front of the school. We will be making candles in June to display that night. The candles will be lit from 7:00 to 8:30 pm. We will be having snow cones and enjoying each others company.

連絡先：
For more information, please see our website. www.shinurayasupreschool.com
